# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend environment variables — EXAMPLE (copy to .env)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# No environment variables are required for the frontend.
# API calls use a relative /api path which works on both Vercel and
# local dev (via Vite's built-in proxy in vite.config.js).
#
# If you ever need to point to a different API host (e.g. a staging API
# on a different domain), you can set:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-staging-api.example.com/api
